parameters: Due to a curse of magic, Anastasia has lost her magical powers.

It is possible to regain magical powers by defeating enemies and
leveling up.
Enemies will appear inside the witch's mansion.

There are facilities inside the witch's mansion that make it easy to
level up.

In this world, there is no concept of staying overnight to heal
injuries.

Physical strength and consumed magical power can only be recovered
through sorcery and items.
Items can be purchased at the town's shop.

Furthermore, Anastasia possesses valuable items that can restore her
health.

During battle, you cannot use it, but it will not disappear even if
you use it.
The libido gauge has been added.

The libido gauge will increase every time you move on the map. This
does not include movement inside buildings.

When the gauge is filled to the maximum, it will transition to an
event to release sexual desire.
Depending on the situation, the gauge may fill up more easily.

You will clear the game by advancing through the event until the end
or by defeating the witch.
